data.description: Come see this 2 story, corner 3BR 2 1/2BA townhome located in the GATED community of Williams Preserve. The private entrance leads you to an open Living Room/Kitchen concept. Kitchen features stainless appliances, tile floors, granite countertops and 42" wood cabinets. Eat-in in dining space has corner windows that offer lots of natural light and a closet pantry. Overlooking the breakfast bar is your main living area with 10ft ceilings, modern paint colors and tile floors. Enjoy the water/ preserve views from your private, corner screened lanai. Under the stairs you will find 1/2 bath and 2 large storage closet. All 3 bedrooms are upstairs and have custom blackout shades. Primary suite has carpet, an oversized walk-in closet w/custom closet system and views of the preserve. Primary bathroom has dual sinks and a spacious shower. Laundry closet is conveniently located upstairs. 2 additional bedrooms share a full bath with tub/ shower combo. Gated community offers playground and swimming pool.  Location, location, location ...quick access to 27,  I4 , 192, Disney Theme Parks, restaurants, hospitals, banks and more.
